<verse sid="NUM 7:58"/>and one male goat from the goats for sin,<verse eid="NUM 7:58"/>

<verse sid="NUM 7:59"/>and for an offering of deliverance two heifers, five rams, five male goats, five year-old ewe lambs. This was the gift of Gamaliel son of Phadasour.<verse eid="NUM 7:59"/>

<verse sid="NUM 7:60"/>On the ninth day, as ruler of the sons of Beniamin, Abidan son of Gadeoni.<verse eid="NUM 7:60"/>

