<verse sid="NUM 7:64"/>and one male goat from the goats for sin,<verse eid="NUM 7:64"/>

<verse sid="NUM 7:65"/>and for an offering of deliverance two heifers, five rams, five male goats, five year-old ewe lambs. This was the gift of Abidan son of Gadeoni.<verse eid="NUM 7:65"/>

