<verse sid="NUM 7:84"/>This was the dedication of the altar, on the day on which he anointed it, from the rulers of the sons of Israel: twelve silver bowls, twelve silver saucers, twelve golden censers,<verse eid="NUM 7:84"/>

<verse sid="NUM 7:85"/>each bowl a hundred thirty shekels and each saucer seventy shekels-- all the silver of the vessels two thousand and four hundred shekels by the shekel of the holy things,<verse eid="NUM 7:85"/>

